{
  "stem": "4345.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "One son was from Monowitz-Auschwitz, who came to Chrzanow-- he lived there before the war-- and this boy, [?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Shamusan. ?] So the three of them died on the gallows.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 39,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And then, there was this boy, 18 years old, so it's four and three other people, just people at random they picked for the-- for this-- for this hanging.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "My then-- then-- then, we had a Schindler also, by the way, but not the Schindler.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "His name was Schindler also but one of them from those-- from those Gestapo called Zagorski.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They couldn't say Zagorski but 'Sagorski.' The 'z' was like I said there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he ordered my dad to cut down the bodies.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I remember how gently my daddy had this knife in his hand.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And he cut the rope and then he took the body and put it down.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then, he did the same to the second and gently put it down and then all seven were laid out.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this is all that we could do.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "There was no burial.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "There was nothing.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "If they picked up the bodies later and sent them to the factories where they make soaps, which they did, it's quite possible.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "There were other reasons they-- they used them, you know.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Not reasons-- they used them for many important things, hair for the mattresses, lampshades and-- and soaps.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Sometimes, they shipped it to Germany, the finest soaps they had, you know.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "I came home and I fell done on the floor and I-- and I was hardly-- you know, my mother hardly revived me already.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "She thought I'm dead.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I could not-- what I saw, what I witnessed was already too much for me to bear.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "I-- I couldn't believe it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was a 19-- oh, I worked in [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
